Install required packages
Bash
Copy code
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y gnupg curl software-properties-common
3️⃣ Add HashiCorp GPG key (Fix for NO_PUBKEY error)
Bash
Copy code
curl -fsSL https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com/gpg | \
sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg
4️⃣ Add HashiCorp repository
Bash
Copy code
echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com noble main" | \
sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/hashicorp.list
5️⃣ Update again
Bash
Copy code
sudo apt update
Now the GPG error should disappear.
6️⃣ Install Terraform
Bash
Copy code
sudo apt install terraform -y
7️⃣ Verify Terraform
Bash
Copy code
terraform -version
Example output:
Copy code

